Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
projects.ruclinic.enhancedgui.ruclinic.Appointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Imaging
public class Appointment extends Object implements Comparable<Appointment>
This class defines the Appointment data type that has the instance variables Date, Timeslot, patient, provider.
Author:
Michael Ehresman, Melissa Xuan
